event.title: Exclusive dinner with Dick Batchelor
event.info: Valued eClub members will be invited to a private dinner with Dick Batchelor. Mr. Batchelor is a former House of Representatives member and has been ranked the 44th most powerful person in Orlando. Only our most active members will be invited to this dinner, so be sure to show your enthusiasm during our speaker and workshop meetings for a chance to attend this special event.

event.title: Cody Simms (Managing Director of TechStars)
event.info: Cody Simms will be speaking with Entrepreneurship Club about his experiences directing TechStars, which is one of the top Startup Accelerators in the world. There will be sure to be much valuable insight into this sector of business.
